snippet.title: Devlog - LATE NIGHT HUNGER
snippet.description:
GAME PAGE➤➤https://tnp-games.itch.io/late-night-hunger

《The process of making Late Night Hunger!
- In development from March 20th till July 19th - 》

You're not alone. A scary figure and past traumas haunt the house, creating terrifying challenges. Face these threats and guide Alex through his fears. Can you solve the mysteries and keep Alex safe until morning?
